kagent deploy {{.Name}} --api-key <your-api-key>


**Option B: Using Kubernetes secret**
Create secret
kubectl create secret generic my-secret -n <namespace>
--from-literal={{.ModelProvider | ToUpper}}_API_KEY=$API_KEY
--dry-run=client -o yaml | kubectl apply -f -

